1
00:01:37,850 --> 00:01:41,039
[The Epoch of Miyu]

2
00:01:41,090 --> 00:01:43,950
[Episode 31]

3
00:01:48,310 --> 00:01:50,070
I've actually imagined many times

4
00:01:50,070 --> 00:01:51,789
what it would be like for us
to be together.

5
00:01:51,789 --> 00:01:53,870
I could talk about art with you,

6
00:01:54,560 --> 00:01:56,640
take you to see exhibitions
all over the world

7
00:01:56,640 --> 00:01:58,500
and give you everything you want.

8
00:01:58,850 --> 00:01:59,759
You'll just need to stay

9
00:01:59,759 --> 00:02:01,090
by my side with no worry.

10
00:02:02,240 --> 00:02:03,040
So, Miyu,

11
00:02:04,260 --> 00:02:05,590
can you give me a chance?

12
00:02:20,360 --> 00:02:21,540
I'm sorry, Mr. Tan.

13
00:02:22,800 --> 00:02:25,130
I cannot accept your pursuit.

14
00:02:27,870 --> 00:02:29,650
Do you have someone you like?

15
00:02:34,920 --> 00:02:36,800
Alright. I got it.

16
00:02:37,970 --> 00:02:39,970
When we spent time together before,

17
00:02:40,620 --> 00:02:42,480
I didn't keep proper boundaries.

18
00:02:42,820 --> 00:02:45,250
I've always said we're friends,

19
00:02:45,310 --> 00:02:46,030
but

20
00:02:47,380 --> 00:02:48,780
actually, I've used you.

21
00:02:49,870 --> 00:02:53,320
To some degree, I've never
been completely honest with you.

22
00:02:54,400 --> 00:02:55,120
I'm sorry.

23
00:02:57,310 --> 00:02:59,180
Actually, you don't need to feel guilty.

24
00:02:59,180 --> 00:03:01,040
Wasn't I also just playing along?

25
00:03:01,850 --> 00:03:02,730
We're even now.

26
00:03:03,410 --> 00:03:03,970
Cheers.

27
00:03:12,310 --> 00:03:14,240
But we can still be friends, right?

28
00:03:14,270 --> 00:03:15,060
Of course.

29
00:03:15,590 --> 00:03:16,590
That's good then.

30
00:03:16,990 --> 00:03:17,829
Let's eat.

31
00:03:46,390 --> 00:03:47,910
-I'm sorry.
-You're here.

32
00:03:48,590 --> 00:03:50,260
I'm late because I overslept.

33
00:03:52,280 --> 00:03:54,410
You guys are doing pretty well.

34
00:03:54,880 --> 00:03:55,800
Is that steamer of food ready?

35
00:03:55,800 --> 00:03:58,220
Bring it over here for Chef Jiao
to take a look.

36
00:03:58,220 --> 00:04:00,680
I created a new dish today.

37
00:04:00,700 --> 00:04:01,650
Please taste it.

38
00:04:08,130 --> 00:04:09,100
This one.

39
00:04:23,830 --> 00:04:26,060
[Position and Employment Term]
[Employment Term: 3 Months]

40
00:04:23,950 --> 00:04:25,940
The contract is for 3 months.

41
00:04:26,370 --> 00:04:27,840
Then what will happen
after these 3 months?

42
00:04:27,840 --> 00:04:29,160
By that time,

43
00:04:29,180 --> 00:04:32,580
it depends on whether the hotel
wants to renew your contract.

44
00:04:33,260 --> 00:04:35,190
Why didn't I think of this earlier?

45
00:04:35,310 --> 00:04:37,310
Just like the beans
spilled from a bamboo tube,

46
00:04:37,310 --> 00:04:38,800
I held nothing back.

47
00:04:38,890 --> 00:04:40,950
I haven't even been paid for 2 months,

48
00:04:41,159 --> 00:04:42,670
and my apprentice
is already fully trained.

49
00:04:42,670 --> 00:04:43,540
What should I do?

50
00:04:43,540 --> 00:04:44,560
What can you do?

51
00:04:44,840 --> 00:04:46,540
If the hotel
doesn't want to renew your contract,

52
00:04:46,540 --> 00:04:47,890
then you'll just have to go home.

53
00:04:47,890 --> 00:04:49,159
Are you kidding me?

54
00:04:49,180 --> 00:04:51,690
My unique skill
is only worth tens of thousands of yuan?

55
00:04:51,690 --> 00:04:53,890
This is not okay. I have to call your dad.

56
00:04:54,730 --> 00:04:55,840
Gosh.

57
00:04:59,220 --> 00:05:00,240
Welcome.

58
00:05:00,260 --> 00:05:01,540
Welcome.

59
00:05:11,560 --> 00:05:12,590
Hello, sir.

60
00:05:12,620 --> 00:05:14,350
You can check in at the counter.

61
00:05:15,160 --> 00:05:17,540
I-I'm here to find...

62
00:05:17,670 --> 00:05:18,470
Xu...

63
00:05:21,640 --> 00:05:22,700
Xu Miyu.

64
00:05:22,800 --> 00:05:23,680
Okay.

65
00:05:28,910 --> 00:05:29,710
Miyu.

66
00:05:30,310 --> 00:05:30,950
Miyu.

67
00:05:30,970 --> 00:05:32,170
Please wait a moment.

68
00:05:35,490 --> 00:05:36,090
It's done.

69
00:05:36,100 --> 00:05:36,810
Thank you.

70
00:05:39,310 --> 00:05:39,740
Dad.

71
00:05:39,800 --> 00:05:40,250
You're busy, huh?

72
00:05:40,250 --> 00:05:41,210
When did you arrive?

73
00:05:41,210 --> 00:05:42,640
I just got here.

74
00:05:43,970 --> 00:05:44,880
Well,

75
00:05:45,120 --> 00:05:47,970
I don't even know where to start.

76
00:05:48,640 --> 00:05:51,280
Last time, I was just too angry

77
00:05:51,310 --> 00:05:52,800
and took it all out on you.

78
00:05:52,820 --> 00:05:53,970
It was my fault.

79
00:05:54,000 --> 00:05:54,680
D-Don't...

80
00:05:54,710 --> 00:05:57,020
It's okay. Dad, don't mention it anymore.

81
00:05:57,020 --> 00:05:58,150
It's all in the past.

82
00:05:58,630 --> 00:05:59,800
Okay. I won't mention it again.

83
00:05:59,800 --> 00:06:00,930
It's all in the past.

84
00:06:02,010 --> 00:06:04,330
I've heard you're doing well at the hotel.

85
00:06:04,330 --> 00:06:05,790
You're even a manager now.

86
00:06:06,820 --> 00:06:08,910
That's great. I'm happy for you.

87
00:06:10,230 --> 00:06:11,990
As for your live stream,

88
00:06:12,400 --> 00:06:14,490
wow, all the neighbors watched it.

89
00:06:14,520 --> 00:06:16,460
They all said you looked even prettier
and more elegant

90
00:06:16,460 --> 00:06:17,790
than those superstars.

91
00:06:19,410 --> 00:06:21,870
I knew you would be successful.

92
00:06:22,450 --> 00:06:24,780
You've really won honor for our Xu family.

93
00:06:26,230 --> 00:06:27,960
You're much better than Miyao.

94
00:06:28,490 --> 00:06:30,050
Ms. Xu! Ms. Xu!

95
00:06:30,190 --> 00:06:31,720
The switchboard room
needs you for a moment.

96
00:06:31,720 --> 00:06:33,450
Copy that. I'll be right there.

97
00:06:33,450 --> 00:06:35,730
Dad, go wait in Mom's room first.

98
00:06:35,750 --> 00:06:37,550
I've already booked a table for you
at the Chinese restaurant.

99
00:06:37,550 --> 00:06:39,080
Just mention my name later.

100
00:06:39,159 --> 00:06:39,620
Come on.

101
00:06:39,620 --> 00:06:39,840
Okay.

102
00:06:39,840 --> 00:06:40,520
Follow me.

103
00:06:41,870 --> 00:06:42,200
Well,

104
00:06:42,220 --> 00:06:43,510
let... let me carry this.

105
00:06:43,510 --> 00:06:44,460
-It's okay.
-It's quite heavy.

106
00:06:44,460 --> 00:06:45,020
Let me carry it.

107
00:06:45,020 --> 00:06:47,710
You have something else to do.
Give it to me first.

108
00:06:47,710 --> 00:06:48,600
Let me carry it.

109
00:06:51,540 --> 00:06:53,890
Why didn't you stop your dad
from coming here?

110
00:06:53,890 --> 00:06:55,159
Aren't you afraid the two of them

111
00:06:55,159 --> 00:06:56,820
will stop Mr. Ji at the office door

112
00:06:56,820 --> 00:06:58,280
and just ask him for money?

113
00:06:58,380 --> 00:07:01,470
I know, but he's my dad after all.

114
00:07:01,500 --> 00:07:03,780
What's more, he said my mom's contract
would expire soon,

115
00:07:03,780 --> 00:07:05,050
so he wanted to come and pick her up.

116
00:07:05,050 --> 00:07:06,660
He also said
he wanted to take this chance to visit me.

117
00:07:06,660 --> 00:07:07,980
How could I refuse?

118
00:07:08,190 --> 00:07:10,570
Anyway, judging by this situation,
it's definitely nothing good.

119
00:07:10,570 --> 00:07:11,880
You have to be careful.

120
00:07:13,720 --> 00:07:14,600
Qiaoqi.

121
00:07:15,080 --> 00:07:16,120
Just take them.

122
00:07:16,210 --> 00:07:17,090
Thanks.

123
00:07:26,930 --> 00:07:28,930
I thought about it carefully later.

124
00:07:29,430 --> 00:07:31,130
What you said makes sense.

125
00:07:31,750 --> 00:07:32,870
All these clauses

126
00:07:32,900 --> 00:07:34,530
were written by lawyers.

127
00:07:34,560 --> 00:07:36,820
There are no loopholes we can make use of.

128
00:07:41,950 --> 00:07:43,080
I should be content.

129
00:07:44,010 --> 00:07:46,400
Having worked as a chef in such a

130
00:07:46,430 --> 00:07:47,670
five-star hotel,

131
00:07:48,310 --> 00:07:49,310
I'll have much

132
00:07:49,350 --> 00:07:51,350
to brag about for the rest of my life.

133
00:07:51,740 --> 00:07:53,620
Come on.
Let's drink a toast to our teacher.

134
00:07:53,620 --> 00:07:57,590
-Thank you! Cheers!
-Cheers!

135
00:08:12,210 --> 00:08:14,130
This portion of boat pastries
is called Qinhuai Lifestyle.

136
00:08:14,130 --> 00:08:14,940
Please enjoy.

137
00:08:18,920 --> 00:08:20,700
This is created by my apprentice,

138
00:08:20,700 --> 00:08:21,900
Chef Bao.

139
00:08:22,160 --> 00:08:23,180
I've tasted it.

140
00:08:23,210 --> 00:08:24,470
It's quite delicious.

141
00:08:24,550 --> 00:08:26,480
Taste this to see how it is.

142
00:08:28,600 --> 00:08:32,000
What kind of nonsense
have you been blabbering about?

143
00:08:35,600 --> 00:08:37,690
What did I say wrong again?

144
00:08:40,030 --> 00:08:41,870
"Teach the apprentice, starve the master."

145
00:08:41,870 --> 00:08:43,600
Don't you know this old saying?

146
00:08:44,520 --> 00:08:46,630
You're stupid and undereducated.

147
00:08:47,830 --> 00:08:49,070
What should I do then?

148
00:08:50,580 --> 00:08:54,060
I'm here to get justice for you.

149
00:08:56,050 --> 00:08:57,630
None of them can take your cooking skills

150
00:08:57,630 --> 00:08:58,510
lightly.

151
00:09:15,060 --> 00:09:15,780
Ms. Xu.

152
00:09:19,870 --> 00:09:21,470
Are you looking for someone?

153
00:09:21,640 --> 00:09:23,170
I'm looking for my parents.

154
00:09:23,310 --> 00:09:24,320
I've just promised them

155
00:09:24,320 --> 00:09:26,100
I'll take them out for a walk after work.

156
00:09:26,100 --> 00:09:27,450
But they're not in their room.

157
00:09:27,450 --> 00:09:29,750
I thought they came to the lobby
to wait for me.

158
00:09:29,750 --> 00:09:30,770
They haven't been here.

159
00:09:30,770 --> 00:09:32,630
There aren't many people
in the lobby this morning,

160
00:09:32,630 --> 00:09:33,800
and I've been here the whole time.

161
00:09:33,800 --> 00:09:34,580
If they had come,

162
00:09:34,580 --> 00:09:36,240
I would definitely remember.

163
00:09:36,800 --> 00:09:38,310
Where are they?

164
00:09:38,660 --> 00:09:39,730
They're not in the restaurant, either.

165
00:09:39,730 --> 00:09:41,580
Nor did they reply to my WeChat messages.

166
00:09:41,580 --> 00:09:43,930
Where... Where are they?

167
00:09:47,730 --> 00:09:57,320
[Purong Hotel]

168
00:09:47,890 --> 00:09:50,560
Mr. Ji, regarding my skills,

169
00:09:50,630 --> 00:09:54,030
if you take them away just like that...

170
00:09:55,550 --> 00:09:57,480
We agreed to properly thank Mr. Ji

171
00:09:57,480 --> 00:09:59,390
before we leave.

172
00:09:59,660 --> 00:10:01,670
What nonsense are you talking about now?

173
00:10:01,670 --> 00:10:03,550
Didn't you tell me to say...

174
00:10:03,780 --> 00:10:04,540
I...

175
00:10:04,980 --> 00:10:07,470
What did I tell you to say?

176
00:10:07,750 --> 00:10:10,600
You've been chattering to me
in the past few days,

177
00:10:10,620 --> 00:10:12,840
saying how well
the boat pastries are selling,

178
00:10:12,840 --> 00:10:14,670
and that what you've contributed
isn't physical labor

179
00:10:14,670 --> 00:10:16,260
but an intangible cultural heritage skill.

180
00:10:16,260 --> 00:10:18,010
I only asked her this one question.

181
00:10:18,010 --> 00:10:20,010
I said, "Isn't your hotel's revenue

182
00:10:20,210 --> 00:10:22,660
connected to the employees' performance?"

183
00:10:22,660 --> 00:10:24,850
Didn't I only ask you this one question?

184
00:10:24,850 --> 00:10:25,800
And what are you doing now?

185
00:10:25,800 --> 00:10:27,920
You're here asking for money.

186
00:10:28,070 --> 00:10:30,230
I don't know.

187
00:10:31,010 --> 00:10:33,010
I think I understand what you mean.

188
00:10:34,750 --> 00:10:37,320
Chef Jiao's boat pastries
became a smash hit,

189
00:10:37,340 --> 00:10:40,630
directly contributing to half the success
of our F&B Department.

190
00:10:40,630 --> 00:10:42,630
Although our hotel generously offered

191
00:10:42,630 --> 00:10:44,000
the highest pay in the market to hire her,

192
00:10:44,000 --> 00:10:45,860
Chef Jiao is still not satisfied.

193
00:10:45,880 --> 00:10:46,510
Right?

194
00:10:46,610 --> 00:10:47,530
Yes, yes, yes.

195
00:10:47,670 --> 00:10:48,930
That's exactly what I mean.

196
00:10:48,930 --> 00:10:49,690
Look.

197
00:10:49,900 --> 00:10:51,950
Mr. Ji is a perceptive man.

198
00:10:53,660 --> 00:10:54,500
Mr. Ji,

199
00:10:54,520 --> 00:10:56,920
please don't blame me
for talking too much.

200
00:10:57,540 --> 00:10:59,320
Regarding the pay offered to hire her,

201
00:10:59,320 --> 00:11:01,420
the hotel has indeed been generous enough.

202
00:11:01,420 --> 00:11:02,670
We've witnessed it

203
00:11:02,670 --> 00:11:03,730
and kept it in mind.

204
00:11:04,150 --> 00:11:06,690
But after the success
of the boat pastries,

205
00:11:06,720 --> 00:11:09,480
the hotel hasn't shown any appreciation,

206
00:11:09,760 --> 00:11:13,290
which definitely hurts our feelings a bit.

207
00:11:13,510 --> 00:11:15,280
-We just feel...
-I feel quite upset.

208
00:11:15,280 --> 00:11:17,870
It feels like you'll get rid of us
once you've finished using us.

209
00:11:17,870 --> 00:11:18,680
Right?

210
00:11:21,740 --> 00:11:28,070
[Purong Hotel]

211
00:11:22,830 --> 00:11:25,080
Look. We've contributed

212
00:11:25,110 --> 00:11:26,510
the cooking skills.

213
00:11:26,900 --> 00:11:28,310
The employment term
will also be over soon.

214
00:11:28,310 --> 00:11:30,390
Then we'll just take
tens of thousands of yuan

215
00:11:30,390 --> 00:11:31,240
of employment fees

216
00:11:31,240 --> 00:11:33,390
and leave with nothing else, huh?

217
00:11:33,550 --> 00:11:35,910
So what is the price in your mind?

218
00:11:37,480 --> 00:11:38,320
100,000 yuan.

219
00:11:40,650 --> 00:11:41,490
200,000 yuan.

220
00:11:47,910 --> 00:11:50,030
With the revenue brought by
Chef Jiao's afternoon tea snacks,

221
00:11:50,030 --> 00:11:51,370
according to the regulations,

222
00:11:51,370 --> 00:11:52,730
if it's converted into a bonus,

223
00:11:52,730 --> 00:11:54,680
the hotel can offer 150,000 yuan.

224
00:11:55,790 --> 00:11:58,790
The remaining 50,000 yuan
will be considered as my personal

225
00:11:58,790 --> 00:12:00,970
gratitude to Chef Jiao
for her valuable guidance.

226
00:12:00,970 --> 00:12:02,100
200,000 yuan, deal.

227
00:12:05,030 --> 00:12:06,390
But I have a condition.

228
00:12:07,330 --> 00:12:08,570
Go ahead.

229
00:12:13,890 --> 00:12:14,640
What?

230
00:12:15,510 --> 00:12:17,080
We need to use this 200,000 yuan

231
00:12:17,080 --> 00:12:18,890
to pay off my daughter's debt?

232
00:12:18,990 --> 00:12:19,790
That's right.

233
00:12:20,190 --> 00:12:20,920
Mr. Ji,

234
00:12:20,950 --> 00:12:22,730
I-I understand what you mean.

235
00:12:23,790 --> 00:12:26,630
You've helped us arrange the use
of this money in advance.

236
00:12:26,630 --> 00:12:27,510
However,

237
00:12:28,600 --> 00:12:31,100
as they say,
every family has its own problems.

238
00:12:31,100 --> 00:12:33,000
T-This debt is

239
00:12:33,000 --> 00:12:35,200
our family's private matter after all.

240
00:12:35,390 --> 00:12:37,440
As for who will pay the debt,

241
00:12:37,440 --> 00:12:39,190
how we'll pay it
and how much should be paid,

242
00:12:39,190 --> 00:12:41,390
you really don't need to worry about it.

243
00:12:41,560 --> 00:12:43,320
But these personal debts

244
00:12:43,340 --> 00:12:44,190
have affected

245
00:12:44,250 --> 00:12:46,510
our hotel employee's work performance.

246
00:12:46,570 --> 00:12:48,000
She's always worried,

247
00:12:48,000 --> 00:12:49,480
being unable to focus on work,

248
00:12:49,480 --> 00:12:51,860
which has affected
our hotel's performance and revenue.

249
00:12:51,860 --> 00:12:53,420
If I don't care, who will?

250
00:12:53,450 --> 00:12:55,110
Don't worry about that, Mr. Ji.

251
00:12:55,110 --> 00:12:57,480
I know my daughter's personality
perfectly well.

252
00:12:57,480 --> 00:12:59,010
Even if the sky were to fall,

253
00:12:59,080 --> 00:13:01,370
I'm sure she would still work earnestly.

254
00:13:01,390 --> 00:13:02,650
So you just think it's completely fine

255
00:13:02,650 --> 00:13:04,110
to throw the burden on her?

256
00:13:04,550 --> 00:13:05,550
Do you know

257
00:13:05,800 --> 00:13:06,870
she used her own credit

258
00:13:06,870 --> 00:13:08,070
to guarantee for you?

259
00:13:08,120 --> 00:13:09,410
Due to her trust in you,

260
00:13:09,510 --> 00:13:10,870
she made the sacrifice.

261
00:13:12,410 --> 00:13:15,160
Mr. Ji, we country folks
don't know how to talk properly.

262
00:13:15,160 --> 00:13:16,510
But please rest assured.

263
00:13:16,510 --> 00:13:17,630
She's our own daughter,

264
00:13:17,630 --> 00:13:19,080
and we know her well.

265
00:13:19,400 --> 00:13:21,560
She has the ability to pay off this debt.

266
00:13:21,560 --> 00:13:23,020
After all, when she borrowed the money,

267
00:13:23,020 --> 00:13:24,870
she was still a rich man's wife,
wasn't she?

268
00:13:24,870 --> 00:13:26,380
But she isn't anymore.

269
00:13:26,410 --> 00:13:28,020
Since she has moved on,

270
00:13:28,180 --> 00:13:30,510
why are you two
still stuck in an illusion?

271
00:13:32,520 --> 00:13:33,810
W-We...

272
00:13:55,220 --> 00:13:57,130
Today is a great day.

273
00:13:57,370 --> 00:13:58,730
The three of us

274
00:13:58,760 --> 00:14:00,170
should celebrate properly.

275
00:14:00,170 --> 00:14:00,720
Come on. Cheers.

276
00:14:00,720 --> 00:14:01,160
Cheers.

277
00:14:01,160 --> 00:14:01,690
Cheers.

278
00:14:01,980 --> 00:14:02,550
Cheers!

279
00:14:02,580 --> 00:14:03,390
Let's drink a toast.

280
00:14:03,390 --> 00:14:03,970
Cheers.

281
00:14:05,010 --> 00:14:06,410
What are we celebrating?

282
00:14:06,480 --> 00:14:10,940
We're celebrating your mom's successful
completion of her job at Purong Hotel.

283
00:14:11,670 --> 00:14:14,170
Alright. Let me tell you.
I've thought it over.

284
00:14:14,170 --> 00:14:16,410
While the boat pastries are still popular,

285
00:14:16,410 --> 00:14:19,200
let's hurry back to the guesthouse
and do some marketing, too.

286
00:14:19,200 --> 00:14:21,410
Firstly, we can set up a decorative wall

287
00:14:21,440 --> 00:14:22,720
and cover it with photos.

288
00:14:22,720 --> 00:14:24,310
What kind of photos?

289
00:14:24,340 --> 00:14:26,740
Your work photos at the hotel.

290
00:14:26,770 --> 00:14:28,670
Your photos
with the hotel management staff.

291
00:14:28,670 --> 00:14:29,600
And previously,

292
00:14:29,840 --> 00:14:31,910
weren't there some large-scale events
in your hotel?

293
00:14:31,910 --> 00:14:33,210
Didn't you take photos with those VIPs

294
00:14:33,210 --> 00:14:34,770
and guests?

295
00:14:34,800 --> 00:14:36,440
Wouldn't that be too vulgar?

296
00:14:37,010 --> 00:14:38,250
Don't worry.

297
00:14:38,270 --> 00:14:39,970
The vulgarest things
are the most effective.

298
00:14:39,970 --> 00:14:41,850
Right? Guests just like that.

299
00:14:42,470 --> 00:14:43,270
Oh, by the way.

300
00:14:43,290 --> 00:14:45,330
when we get back there,
I also need to see Li first.

301
00:14:45,330 --> 00:14:46,470
Isn't his son running

302
00:14:46,470 --> 00:14:48,330
a matchmaking agency in our town?

303
00:14:48,390 --> 00:14:49,480
We'll pay him some money

304
00:14:49,480 --> 00:14:52,180
and ask him
to shoot a good promo video for you.

305
00:14:52,400 --> 00:14:54,940
We'll just play it on a loop
in the guesthouse restaurant

306
00:14:54,940 --> 00:14:56,090
to promote our place properly.

307
00:14:56,090 --> 00:14:57,630
That's a great idea. I like it.

308
00:14:57,630 --> 00:14:58,210
Okay.

309
00:14:59,150 --> 00:15:00,700
Dad, Mom.

310
00:15:02,220 --> 00:15:05,880
There's still a network loan
of over 200,000 yuan for me to pay off.

311
00:15:07,480 --> 00:15:09,900
Don't you have to pay
only 5,000 yuan a month?

312
00:15:09,900 --> 00:15:12,420
Only 5,000 yuan? Will you pay the money?

313
00:15:12,750 --> 00:15:13,630
Of course.

314
00:15:14,630 --> 00:15:16,370
If we have the money,
we'll definitely pay.

315
00:15:16,370 --> 00:15:17,730
Then pay the debt now.

316
00:15:17,750 --> 00:15:19,150
Don't you have money now?

317
00:15:20,840 --> 00:15:23,910
-What... What money?
-You asked Mr. Ji for 200,000 yuan.

318
00:15:23,910 --> 00:15:24,970
I know everything.

319
00:15:27,420 --> 00:15:31,130
That sum of money is another matter.

320
00:15:32,370 --> 00:15:34,090
You know what? Now we've met another...

321
00:15:34,090 --> 00:15:35,890
Just treat me as a nuisance, too.

322
00:15:38,010 --> 00:15:40,470
Consider that 200,000 yuan
as my hush money.

323
00:15:41,440 --> 00:15:43,640
I'll figure out a way to pay off the rest.

324
00:15:44,240 --> 00:15:46,340
In the future, I won't ask you two
for money anymore.

325
00:15:46,340 --> 00:15:47,980
This network loan of over 300,000 yuan

326
00:15:47,980 --> 00:15:49,730
can be paid off with just 200,000 yuan.

327
00:15:49,730 --> 00:15:51,700
You can even make a net profit
of 100,000 yuan.

328
00:15:51,700 --> 00:15:52,780
It's such a good deal, isn't it?

329
00:15:52,780 --> 00:15:55,440
W-What are you talking about?

330
00:15:55,900 --> 00:15:57,940
Why do you sound so distant?

331
00:15:58,000 --> 00:16:00,990
It sounds as if you were trying to
distance yourself from us.

332
00:16:00,990 --> 00:16:02,320
Hearing you say that,

333
00:16:02,340 --> 00:16:04,080
I feel a bit hurt.

334
00:16:04,150 --> 00:16:05,570
Don't make such jokes anymore.

335
00:16:05,570 --> 00:16:06,900
I'm not joking with you.

336
00:16:07,630 --> 00:16:09,160
This 200,000 yuan is yours.

337
00:16:10,250 --> 00:16:11,750
The network loan of over 300,000 yuan
I've borrowed

338
00:16:11,750 --> 00:16:12,630
is also yours.

339
00:16:13,240 --> 00:16:14,730
Even I am yours.

340
00:16:15,810 --> 00:16:16,650
Does it matter

341
00:16:17,710 --> 00:16:19,190
who I am?

342
00:16:19,750 --> 00:16:21,030
When I had the ability,

343
00:16:21,030 --> 00:16:22,630
I helped you two build a guesthouse

344
00:16:22,630 --> 00:16:23,680
and pay the network loan.

345
00:16:23,680 --> 00:16:26,330
After I lost that ability,
I have to make a living myself

346
00:16:26,330 --> 00:16:27,530
and survive on my own.

347
00:16:27,830 --> 00:16:29,640
Dad, Mom.

348
00:16:30,520 --> 00:16:32,120
When you were using me,

349
00:16:32,140 --> 00:16:34,000
had you ever loved me for a moment?

350
00:16:34,270 --> 00:16:35,390
Miyu,

351
00:16:35,640 --> 00:16:38,020
what you said isn't nice.

352
00:16:38,120 --> 00:16:39,120
No matter what,

353
00:16:39,270 --> 00:16:40,810
we've brought you up after all, right?

354
00:16:40,810 --> 00:16:41,220
Yes.

355
00:16:42,180 --> 00:16:43,640
You've been telling me you brought me up

356
00:16:43,640 --> 00:16:45,500
for as many years as you raised me.

357
00:16:46,590 --> 00:16:47,750
I was just too grateful

358
00:16:47,750 --> 00:16:49,030
and felt too guilty,

359
00:16:49,370 --> 00:16:51,320
so I tried so hard to leave the village

360
00:16:51,320 --> 00:16:52,870
and marry into the city

361
00:16:53,390 --> 00:16:55,440
to repay your kindness.

362
00:16:56,150 --> 00:16:57,080
Only until now have I realized

363
00:16:57,080 --> 00:16:57,960
I was so stupid.

364
00:16:58,670 --> 00:17:00,190
All you want is money.

365
00:17:00,790 --> 00:17:01,910
Gratitude and guilt

366
00:17:01,910 --> 00:17:03,750
were the password
you used to withdraw money

367
00:17:03,750 --> 00:17:05,280
from me, who was like an ATM.

368
00:17:06,069 --> 00:17:06,829
From today onwards,

369
00:17:06,829 --> 00:17:08,270
this password is cancelled.

370
00:17:08,270 --> 00:17:09,750
From now on,
if it's about money, we discuss money,

371
00:17:09,750 --> 00:17:11,950
and if it's about matters,
we discuss matters.

372
00:17:11,950 --> 00:17:13,750
This way, it's easier for us all.

373
00:17:13,760 --> 00:17:14,480
Miyu,

374
00:17:14,480 --> 00:17:16,000
aren't you my daughter?

375
00:17:16,000 --> 00:17:17,020
Yes, I am.

376
00:17:17,270 --> 00:17:19,079
Of course I am your daughter.

377
00:17:19,530 --> 00:17:21,290
I am your biological daughter.

378
00:17:23,720 --> 00:17:25,160
I will always be grateful

379
00:17:25,349 --> 00:17:27,980
to you two for raising me.

380
00:17:28,170 --> 00:17:29,160
But that doesn't mean

381
00:17:29,160 --> 00:17:30,160
I have to spend my whole life

382
00:17:30,160 --> 00:17:31,880
paying for both of your lives

383
00:17:32,750 --> 00:17:36,090
and bearing
your self-righteous plundering.

384
00:18:42,240 --> 00:18:42,960
[Message]

385
00:18:42,980 --> 00:18:46,140
[Consumer Finance:
Your business loan has been paid with]

386
00:18:46,170 --> 00:18:50,300
[5,000 yuan ahead of time successfully.]
[The payment has been settled this month.]

387
00:19:14,450 --> 00:19:16,130
Are you off work, Ms. Xu?

388
00:19:17,330 --> 00:19:18,130
Get in the car.

389
00:19:30,560 --> 00:19:31,390
Thank you.

390
00:19:39,600 --> 00:19:41,520
Ms. Xu, I'm sorry

391
00:19:41,680 --> 00:19:44,210
for suddenly asking you
to have a meal with me.

392
00:19:44,610 --> 00:19:45,440
It's alright.

393
00:19:45,460 --> 00:19:48,190
Ms. Jiang,
I should thank you for the invitation.

394
00:19:48,670 --> 00:19:50,110
I'm not very good at cooking.

395
00:19:50,110 --> 00:19:52,270
I usually either order takeout

396
00:19:52,330 --> 00:19:54,330
or cook a small pot of rice

397
00:19:54,360 --> 00:19:55,590
and eat it with some side dishes

398
00:19:55,590 --> 00:19:56,920
to grab a bite casually.

399
00:19:57,460 --> 00:19:58,240
Oh, by the way,

400
00:19:58,240 --> 00:19:59,400
let me formally introduce to you

401
00:19:59,400 --> 00:20:00,720
my favorite side dishes for rice.

402
00:20:00,720 --> 00:20:02,830
If you like quick pickles,

403
00:20:02,850 --> 00:20:05,050
you can taste this bowl of sour celtuce.

404
00:20:08,010 --> 00:20:09,160
Is this celtuce?

405
00:20:10,670 --> 00:20:12,290
It's a kind of mixed pickles.

406
00:20:12,400 --> 00:20:14,730
It's a very common brand in supermarkets.

407
00:20:15,140 --> 00:20:17,530
The radish inside is soft,

408
00:20:17,550 --> 00:20:19,040
and the cabbage is a bit too salty.

409
00:20:19,040 --> 00:20:20,280
But only this celtuce

410
00:20:20,310 --> 00:20:21,600
is pickled just right.

411
00:20:21,620 --> 00:20:23,290
It's crisp and sour,

412
00:20:23,350 --> 00:20:25,680
just like a breath of fresh air
in the mess.

413
00:20:25,780 --> 00:20:27,580
Pickles are really amazing.

414
00:20:27,600 --> 00:20:28,770
They don't wait for anyone.

415
00:20:28,770 --> 00:20:31,040
If you eat them at their best time,

416
00:20:31,070 --> 00:20:33,930
it's even more wonderful
than winning the lottery.

417
00:20:34,610 --> 00:20:35,960
At their best time.

418
00:20:36,950 --> 00:20:37,860
Ms. Xu.

419
00:20:38,280 --> 00:20:40,810
You always say things that deeply move me.

420
00:20:41,810 --> 00:20:44,340
Ms. Jiang,
aren't you at your best time now?

421
00:20:44,650 --> 00:20:46,510
Speaking of a person's best time,

422
00:20:48,060 --> 00:20:50,390
perhaps only the person knows it himself.

423
00:20:50,720 --> 00:20:52,920
Maybe it's not the most glorious moment

424
00:20:53,140 --> 00:20:54,660
that outsiders can see.

425
00:20:55,210 --> 00:20:58,790
Nor is it the time
when one is full of hope for the future.

426
00:20:58,810 --> 00:21:01,520
It's not even the time
of financial freedom

427
00:21:01,550 --> 00:21:03,210
or spiritual freedom.

428
00:21:03,300 --> 00:21:04,620
Rather, it's the time

429
00:21:05,960 --> 00:21:08,020
when that very person is by your side.

430
00:21:11,960 --> 00:21:13,290
Ms. Xu.

431
00:21:15,880 --> 00:21:18,210
I asked Mr. Ji
to get back together with me.

432
00:21:22,690 --> 00:21:23,610
Is that so?

433
00:21:24,240 --> 00:21:25,290
What do you think?

434
00:21:28,480 --> 00:21:29,930
I think it's great.

435
00:21:30,190 --> 00:21:31,550
You two are a good match.

436
00:21:32,080 --> 00:21:34,080
Aren't you going to ask if he agreed?

437
00:21:36,300 --> 00:21:39,210
I don't think
this has anything to do with me.

438
00:21:43,550 --> 00:21:44,550
Ms. Xu.

439
00:21:44,990 --> 00:21:46,360
You must have heard

440
00:21:46,590 --> 00:21:49,050
that I've been
having some problems lately.

441
00:21:51,570 --> 00:21:52,970
For a moment,

442
00:21:53,350 --> 00:21:54,960
I even thought

443
00:21:55,340 --> 00:21:57,000
it would be better to just die.

444
00:21:57,960 --> 00:21:58,690
Don't worry.

445
00:21:59,070 --> 00:22:00,160
I'm fine.

446
00:22:00,790 --> 00:22:01,590
Fortunately,

447
00:22:01,920 --> 00:22:04,110
Ji Feng found me in time.

448
00:22:04,920 --> 00:22:06,770
I was so happy at that time.

449
00:22:07,070 --> 00:22:07,790
I felt that

450
00:22:08,200 --> 00:22:09,720
he still cared about me.

451
00:22:10,420 --> 00:22:12,020
Even if that wasn't the case,

452
00:22:12,630 --> 00:22:13,460
I thought

453
00:22:14,000 --> 00:22:15,880
seeing me in such a miserable state,

454
00:22:15,880 --> 00:22:16,480
he would at least

455
00:22:16,480 --> 00:22:18,340
say something nice to comfort me.

456
00:22:20,310 --> 00:22:21,510
Guess what

457
00:22:21,790 --> 00:22:23,190
he said to me at that time?

458
00:22:25,250 --> 00:22:26,210
He said

459
00:22:26,880 --> 00:22:28,540
it was impossible between us.

460
00:22:29,610 --> 00:22:31,090
The person he likes is you.

461
00:22:35,550 --> 00:22:36,720
Even though Ji Feng

462
00:22:37,160 --> 00:22:38,970
is usually quite shrewd

463
00:22:39,000 --> 00:22:40,280
in the workplace,

464
00:22:40,990 --> 00:22:42,250
actually, in his daily life,

465
00:22:42,250 --> 00:22:43,510
he's just that simple.

466
00:22:43,830 --> 00:22:45,960
If he likes someone, he just likes her.

467
00:22:46,130 --> 00:22:48,590
If he doesn't like someone,
he just doesn't.

468
00:22:48,640 --> 00:22:50,320
There is no middle ground.

469
00:22:51,530 --> 00:22:53,920
He brought me back here that day

470
00:22:53,940 --> 00:22:55,260
and left right away.

471
00:22:55,470 --> 00:22:57,470
Hailin was also at home at that time.

472
00:22:58,100 --> 00:23:01,300
Being photographed by reporters
was purely an accident.

473
00:23:01,330 --> 00:23:03,130
I hope you won't misunderstand.

474
00:23:07,120 --> 00:23:08,090
Also,

475
00:23:09,820 --> 00:23:10,780
previously,

476
00:23:11,590 --> 00:23:13,640
after the live stream,

477
00:23:13,720 --> 00:23:15,480
I told you those things

478
00:23:16,400 --> 00:23:17,360
because I actually...

479
00:23:17,360 --> 00:23:19,700
wanted to persuade you to leave Ji Feng.

480
00:23:20,550 --> 00:23:22,260
I acted too despicably.

481
00:23:23,160 --> 00:23:24,540
I owe you an apology.

482
00:23:25,960 --> 00:23:26,770
I'm sorry.

483
00:23:28,120 --> 00:23:28,840
Ms. Jiang.

484
00:23:28,860 --> 00:23:29,650
Miyu.

485
00:23:29,920 --> 00:23:31,050
Don't you think

486
00:23:31,970 --> 00:23:33,830
you owe yourself an apology, too?

487
00:23:36,420 --> 00:23:38,680
You're clearly so nice to everyone else,

488
00:23:39,910 --> 00:23:41,850
but not to yourself.

489
00:23:42,440 --> 00:23:44,030
You hold back your hatred

490
00:23:45,110 --> 00:23:46,710
and even suppress your love.

491
00:23:47,850 --> 00:23:49,710
Don't you think that's too cruel?

492
00:23:50,850 --> 00:23:52,580
Those who truly care about you

493
00:23:53,210 --> 00:23:54,650
and want to love you

494
00:23:55,410 --> 00:23:57,210
don't even know what to do.

495
00:23:58,800 --> 00:23:59,640
Look.

496
00:24:01,750 --> 00:24:03,160
The best time

497
00:24:04,400 --> 00:24:06,360
always slips away quietly.

498
00:24:07,640 --> 00:24:10,880
When I was at my best time,

499
00:24:11,240 --> 00:24:13,170
I failed to grasp the essence of it.

500
00:24:13,860 --> 00:24:16,640
Now that I know the essence of it,

501
00:24:17,090 --> 00:24:19,080
everything has changed.

502
00:24:20,160 --> 00:24:21,450
I'm like this

503
00:24:21,750 --> 00:24:23,440
over-pickled radish,

504
00:24:23,830 --> 00:24:26,230
instead of the perfectly pickled celtuce.

505
00:24:26,350 --> 00:24:27,610
But you are different.

506
00:24:29,810 --> 00:24:31,440
Don't let hesitation

507
00:24:32,720 --> 00:24:34,430
make you miss the right time

508
00:24:35,870 --> 00:24:37,070
and the right person.

509
00:24:44,440 --> 00:24:45,950
I got it, Ms. Jiang.

510
00:24:47,780 --> 00:24:48,960
Thank you.

511
00:25:30,090 --> 00:25:31,620
Time cannot be turned back.

512
00:25:32,130 --> 00:25:34,400
Once a path is taken,

513
00:25:34,710 --> 00:25:35,790
it's just taken.

514
00:25:36,770 --> 00:25:38,970
For example, if those documents
are blown away by the wind,

515
00:25:37,000 --> 00:25:40,630
♪ Love is truly not easy to obtain ♪

516
00:25:39,470 --> 00:25:42,160
what we can catch
can only be the next page.

517
00:25:44,380 --> 00:25:48,110
♪ I can't hold on to you
if you want to leave ♪

518
00:25:45,920 --> 00:25:47,070
This is not fair.

519
00:25:48,200 --> 00:25:49,800
I've clearly become better.

520
00:25:49,890 --> 00:25:50,650
Yes.

521
00:25:51,570 --> 00:25:55,480
♪ I tell myself I'm not hurt
once things settle down ♪

522
00:25:51,650 --> 00:25:53,050
The better Jiang Zhichun

523
00:25:53,450 --> 00:25:54,920
deserves a better future,

524
00:25:55,400 --> 00:25:58,200
instead of being trapped
in the past assumptions.

525
00:25:58,980 --> 00:26:02,790
♪ But I realize I can't deceive myself ♪

526
00:25:59,850 --> 00:26:00,640
Yeah.

527
00:26:01,720 --> 00:26:03,780
I should have understood it earlier.

528
00:26:04,280 --> 00:26:05,280
A businessperson

529
00:26:05,770 --> 00:26:08,160
should solve problems in a business way.

530
00:26:06,380 --> 00:26:10,500
♪ I always say
life is already hard enough ♪

531
00:26:08,460 --> 00:26:09,260
For example?

532
00:26:10,530 --> 00:26:14,700
For example,
if they use cyberbullying as a weapon,

533
00:26:14,010 --> 00:26:18,040
♪ So what else is there worth trying for ♪

534
00:26:16,360 --> 00:26:18,080
I should show them

535
00:26:18,800 --> 00:26:20,670
what a real public opinion war is.

536
00:26:21,350 --> 00:26:25,390
♪ Friends comfort me,
telling me to have a drink ♪

537
00:26:22,460 --> 00:26:23,940
That's more like you.

538
00:26:28,640 --> 00:26:30,160
Let me ask you one last question.

539
00:26:28,960 --> 00:26:32,860
♪ But I've already started living
like I'm not myself anymore ♪

540
00:26:36,440 --> 00:26:39,320
♪ I feel reluctant ♪

541
00:26:37,380 --> 00:26:38,560
For all these years,

542
00:26:40,680 --> 00:26:42,160
have you ever had a moment of...

543
00:26:42,160 --> 00:26:42,990
Yes, I have.

544
00:26:42,680 --> 00:26:48,530
♪ I feel reluctant to recall
or forget those memories ♪

545
00:26:45,440 --> 00:26:47,100
But it was exactly those times

546
00:26:48,320 --> 00:26:49,720
that made me more certain

547
00:26:50,230 --> 00:26:52,610
that the best distance between us

548
00:26:51,020 --> 00:26:54,250
♪ I feel reluctant ♪

549
00:26:53,720 --> 00:26:55,060
is just like this now.

550
00:26:57,630 --> 00:27:03,350
♪ I feel reluctant to grab on to anyone
and I can't breathe ♪

551
00:27:04,530 --> 00:27:07,390
♪ I've been indulging myself ♪

552
00:27:06,890 --> 00:27:08,420
Thank you for your honesty.

553
00:27:21,860 --> 00:27:24,820
♪ I feel reluctant ♪

554
00:27:24,990 --> 00:27:25,840
This time,

555
00:27:28,120 --> 00:27:33,970
♪ I feel reluctant to recall
or forget those memories ♪

556
00:27:28,610 --> 00:27:30,410
it's really time to say goodbye.

557
00:27:36,370 --> 00:27:40,380
♪ I feel reluctant ♪

558
00:27:39,740 --> 00:27:40,980
Ms. Xu.

559
00:27:41,800 --> 00:27:43,410
Love is troublesome,

560
00:27:42,200 --> 00:27:47,960
♪ I feel reluctant to grab on to anyone
and I can't breathe ♪

561
00:27:44,030 --> 00:27:46,100
but it's worth our courage.

562
00:27:49,710 --> 00:27:52,230
