563
00:27:52,130 --> 00:27:58,630
[Purong Hotel Staff Apartment]

564
00:28:10,400 --> 00:28:11,250
Hello.

565
00:28:11,510 --> 00:28:12,270
Ji Feng.

566
00:28:12,860 --> 00:28:13,910
Where are you?

567
00:28:14,090 --> 00:28:14,890
Where are you?

568
00:28:15,390 --> 00:28:17,390
I'm on my way to the hotel to find you.

569
00:28:18,070 --> 00:28:19,800
I-I have something to tell you.

570
00:28:19,920 --> 00:28:21,170
I'm downstairs at your dorm.

571
00:28:21,170 --> 00:28:22,050
Wait for me.

572
00:28:38,070 --> 00:28:39,850
-I have something to tell you.
-I have something to tell you.

573
00:28:39,850 --> 00:28:40,950
