574
00:28:41,550 --> 00:28:42,260
Okay.

575
00:28:42,280 --> 00:28:43,240
I admit

576
00:28:43,940 --> 00:28:46,200
in terms of starting a new relationship,

577
00:28:46,550 --> 00:28:47,930
now I'm a bit afraid

578
00:28:47,990 --> 00:28:49,200
and reserved.

579
00:28:50,140 --> 00:28:52,070
I have let myself down for too long.

580
00:28:52,080 --> 00:28:53,230
Right now,

581
00:28:53,480 --> 00:28:56,290
I just want to give all my love
and expectations back to myself.

582
00:28:56,290 --> 00:28:57,300
I am very afraid.

583
00:28:57,690 --> 00:29:00,350
I'm afraid that if I fall in love
with someone again,

584
00:29:00,350 --> 00:29:02,080
I will repeat my past mistakes,

585
00:29:02,820 --> 00:29:05,450
so I've been
looking for all kinds of excuses

586
00:29:05,480 --> 00:29:07,280
to avoid my feelings for you.

587
00:29:07,920 --> 00:29:09,160
But now,

588
00:29:10,020 --> 00:29:11,090
I don't want to

589
00:29:11,570 --> 00:29:13,450
and I can't avoid them anymore.

590
00:29:16,020 --> 00:29:16,820
Ji Feng.

591
00:29:18,690 --> 00:29:20,130
I want to start over

592
00:29:21,830 --> 00:29:22,510
with you.

593
00:29:43,990 --> 00:29:45,920
I'm glad I'm with you finally.

594
00:29:46,740 --> 00:29:48,780
I've also always wanted to tell you

595
00:29:49,550 --> 00:29:51,000
I like you too.

596
00:30:38,890 --> 00:30:41,870
♪ Bury everything in your mind ♪

597
00:30:42,880 --> 00:30:45,730
♪ Hope love blossoms as wished ♪

598
00:30:46,470 --> 00:30:50,040
♪ Rainwater silently nourishes flowers ♪

599
00:30:51,280 --> 00:30:52,380
♪ At its own expense ♪

600
00:30:53,220 --> 00:30:55,400
♪ That fleeting moment I tried to hold ♪

601
00:30:56,250 --> 00:30:59,200
♪ Let it go when the glass runs dry ♪

602
00:31:00,220 --> 00:31:03,140
♪ Unfinished longings ♪

603
00:31:03,880 --> 00:31:06,940
♪ Drift like fading embers ♪

604
00:31:08,130 --> 00:31:10,330
♪ Still longing for yesterday's glow ♪

605
00:31:11,210 --> 00:31:14,020
♪ Yet sailing into
the ocean's depths at night ♪

606
00:31:15,050 --> 00:31:18,130
♪ Questions without answers ♪

607
00:31:19,110 --> 00:31:21,760
♪ Let them go with the wind ♪

608
00:31:23,220 --> 00:31:24,760
♪ Let them go ♪

609
00:31:35,280 --> 00:31:36,140
Morning.

610
00:31:36,360 --> 00:31:37,070
Morning.

611
00:31:46,510 --> 00:31:47,510
Wait.

612
00:31:48,320 --> 00:31:50,890
I don't want to
bring personal feelings into work.

613
00:31:50,890 --> 00:31:52,700
You're still Mr. Ji, the general manager,

614
00:31:52,700 --> 00:31:54,230
and I'm Ms. Xu, the manager.

615
00:31:54,230 --> 00:31:55,960
We're both very professional.

616
00:31:59,640 --> 00:32:00,360
Thank you.

617
00:32:02,480 --> 00:32:05,170
Then let's just talk about business.

618
00:32:06,120 --> 00:32:08,040
You said you wanted to transfer
to the sales department.

619
00:32:08,040 --> 00:32:09,900
Can you give me a specific reason?

620
00:32:12,770 --> 00:32:13,880
I think,

621
00:32:13,900 --> 00:32:16,940
from the jazz performance
at the Western Restaurant last time

622
00:32:16,940 --> 00:32:19,480
to the planning
of the college entrance exam rooms,

623
00:32:19,480 --> 00:32:22,130
I do have some talent for sales.

624
00:32:23,540 --> 00:32:26,280
You do have sales intuition
and execution ability.

625
00:32:26,280 --> 00:32:27,680
But competing with those

626
00:32:27,750 --> 00:32:30,750
top sales reps
who specialize in developing business

627
00:32:30,850 --> 00:32:31,990
is a different thing.

628
00:32:31,990 --> 00:32:32,550
Besides,

629
00:32:32,950 --> 00:32:33,670
sales is

630
00:32:33,690 --> 00:32:35,270
also completely different from

631
00:32:35,270 --> 00:32:36,870
the work you've done before.

632
00:32:36,890 --> 00:32:39,290
As for the methods and tactics
it requires,

633
00:32:39,590 --> 00:32:40,640
are you able to use them?

634
00:32:40,640 --> 00:32:41,830
Everyone is different.

635
00:32:41,830 --> 00:32:43,100
A thousand people have a thousand faces.

636
00:32:43,100 --> 00:32:45,470
I don't think I might be able to be

637
00:32:45,510 --> 00:32:48,160
that kind of aggressive sales rep
who people can't refuse,

638
00:32:48,160 --> 00:32:51,370
but I can understand the products

639
00:32:51,390 --> 00:32:52,730
and learn about the clients,

640
00:32:52,730 --> 00:32:55,430
