how to deal with her.

646
00:33:02,160 --> 00:33:03,570
She's not in my plan.

647
00:33:03,740 --> 00:33:05,550
I have my own mountain to climb.

648
00:33:06,210 --> 00:33:07,220
Okay.

649
00:33:08,390 --> 00:33:11,000
I used to think the hotel industry

650
00:33:11,020 --> 00:33:12,550
was just a

651
