656
00:33:24,480 --> 00:33:25,200
Alright.

657
00:33:26,290 --> 00:33:27,940
Then you have to think it through.

658
00:33:27,940 --> 00:33:28,910
If you join the sales department now,

659
00:33:28,910 --> 00:33:31,530
