663
00:33:36,770 --> 00:33:37,570
Yes, I do.

664
00:33:40,080 --> 00:33:40,840
Come in.

665
00:33:42,480 --> 00:33:43,050
Mr. Ji.

666
00:33:43,310 --> 00:33:44,440
Mr. Wei is here.

667
00:33:45,340 --> 00:33:46,340
Mr. Ji.

668
00:33:46,850 --> 00:33:49,110
