674
00:34:11,230 --> 00:34:11,820
Have a seat.

675
00:34:11,820 --> 00:34:12,969
Let's talk. Come on.

676
00:34:18,739 --> 00:34:21,330
I've recently heard people in the hotel
gossiping about you.

677
00:34:21,330 --> 00:34:21,920
They say you

678
00:34:21,920 --> 00:34:23,880
and Xu Miyu,
the Front Office's lobby manager,

679
00:34:23,880 --> 00:34:25,610
have an unusual relationship.

680
00:34:31,280 --> 00:34:32,340
Actually, I understand.

681
00:34:32,340 --> 00:34:33,370
As a boss,

682
00:34:33,400 --> 00:34:36,060
