687
00:34:45,350 --> 00:34:47,260
Now she's suddenly being transferred
to the sales department.

688
00:34:47,260 --> 00:34:49,449
Her speed is a bit fast.

689
00:34:49,860 --> 00:34:52,260
It's inevitable that people would gossip.

690
00:34:52,280 --> 00:34:53,590
As a housewife

691
