of the executive floor,

705
00:35:24,880 --> 00:35:27,480
I guess no one knows it
better than you, Mr. Wei.

706
00:35:31,460 --> 00:35:32,460
Is that so?

707
00:35:34,240 --> 00:35:35,480
How come I don't remember?

708
00:35:35,480 --> 00:35:37,480
I must be getting old and forgetful.

709
00:35:39,010 --> 00:35:39,970
Perhaps

710
00:35:40,210 --> 00:35:42,160
