714
00:35:49,350 --> 00:35:51,150
has been worthy of her position.

715
00:35:51,340 --> 00:35:53,940
Some even exceeded
everyone's expectations.

716
00:35:54,190 --> 00:35:56,230
And now she has been transferred
to the sales department.

717
00:35:56,230 --> 00:35:57,090
It's also because

718
00:35:57,090 --> 00:35:59,090
