750
00:37:19,000 --> 00:37:20,870
will you have any special...

751
00:37:20,900 --> 00:37:22,290
There are no special arrangements.

752
00:37:22,290 --> 00:37:25,350
Do everything in accordance
with the sales department's rules.

753
00:37:25,350 --> 00:37:26,150
Got it.

754
00:37:26,850 --> 00:37:28,200
It means she should do what she has to do.

755
00:37:28,200 --> 00:37:28,950
Right.

756
00:37:29,950 --> 00:37:30,830
In that case, I am a bit

757
00:37:30,830 --> 00:37:33,160
