758
00:37:33,770 --> 00:37:34,400
Mr. Ji,

759
00:37:34,610 --> 00:37:36,610
I won't take up any more of your time.

760
00:37:38,130 --> 00:37:39,480
No need to see me out.

761
00:37:39,510 --> 00:37:40,250
Goodbye.

762
00:37:40,280 --> 00:37:41,030
Alright.

763
00:37:47,300 --> 00:37:48,100
Mr. Lin.

764
