768
00:37:56,820 --> 00:37:57,680
No.

769
00:37:58,830 --> 00:37:59,410
Alright.

770
00:38:15,420 --> 00:38:16,680
Make some phone calls.

771
00:38:17,150 --> 00:38:18,670
You want me to make phone calls?

772
00:38:18,670 --> 00:38:19,600
Telemarketing.

773
00:38:19,810 --> 00:38:20,940
