827
00:40:20,700 --> 00:40:23,070
What if it grows bigger in the future?

828
00:40:23,660 --> 00:40:26,120
I've seen too many tricks
from such small companies.

829
00:40:26,120 --> 00:40:27,400
If they could sign a contract with you,

830
00:40:27,400 --> 00:40:28,770
why didn't they just sign it?

831
00:40:28,770 --> 00:40:30,580
They just want to come here
for free food and drinks.

832
00:40:30,580 --> 00:40:32,180
That's how telemarketing is like.

833
00:40:32,180 --> 00:40:33,510
The success rate is low.

834
00:40:33,590 --> 00:40:34,840
It's mainly to train you newcomers

835
00:40:34,840 --> 00:40:36,360
so that you guys can open your mouths,
step forward

836
00:40:36,360 --> 00:40:37,720
and unleash your true nature.

837
00:40:37,720 --> 00:40:38,720
Also, Xu,

838
00:40:38,740 --> 00:40:40,010
our department

839
00:40:40,090 --> 00:40:42,150
doesn't expect you to bring in sales.

840
00:40:42,770 --> 00:40:43,900
Don't put too much pressure on yourself.

841
00:40:43,900 --> 00:40:44,660
Okay?

842
00:40:45,960 --> 00:40:47,060
Thank you, Mr. Lin.

843
00:40:47,240 --> 00:40:48,840
I'll think about it further.

844
00:40:48,930 --> 00:40:49,530
Keep it up.
